Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.94,Flashback,Preschooler (Male),0000,0000,0000,,Come over now if you \Nwanna play hide-and-seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:06.44,FlashbackTop,Preschoolers,0000,0000,0000,,Me! I'll play!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:08.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who wonders, \N"Would it be okay for me to join in?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.86,FlashbackTop,Preschoolers,0000,0000,0000,,Me! I'll play!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:16.11,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and so misses her chance, \Nending up all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:12.84,FlashbackTop,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:21.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who ends up all alone at a picnic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:19.73,FlashbackTop,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:24.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,swapping parts of her lunch with the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.38,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who doesn't join any clubs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:33.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,comes home right after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.84,DefaultItalicsTop,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,And here, we'll stir-fry it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:39.02,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and finds her smartphone full of \Nnothing but messages from her parents
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:39.02,DefaultItalicsTop,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of vegetables,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:40.97,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and coupon offers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:42.73,DefaultItalicsTop,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,so you can probably make it quickly \Nif you cut them in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:42.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.35,DefaultItalicsTop,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,You can probably do that \Nin the morning, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:46.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori Goto, first-year in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:46.98,DefaultItalicsTop,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Lately I've gotten good at making \Nso many dishes so quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:49.45,DefaultItalicsTop,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I didn't need to know any more,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.45,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I think
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:51.91,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I should really change the way I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:52.36,DefaultItalicsTop,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,but lately I'm learning once again \Nhow interesting cooking can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:56.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I always stammer when I try to speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:59.05,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm really bad at keeping eye contact...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:02.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A life as the archetypal introvert \Njust seems to fit me best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:02.25,DefaultItalicsTop,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,Personally I like a lot of options with rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:05.11,DefaultItalicsTop,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course. But you—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:03.54,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,You watching this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:05.11,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:11.71,DefaultItalics,Musician,0000,0000,0000,,Back in school, I was the guy who sat in the \Nback of the classroom pretending to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.10,DefaultItalics,Musician,0000,0000,0000,,No friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:18.22,DefaultItalics,Interviewer,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're part of a band that's \Nextremely popular with young people!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:21.56,DefaultItalics,Musician,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A band is a place where \Neven introverts can shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:24.31,DefaultItalics,Interviewer,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:28.77,DefaultItalics,Interviewer,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here's "Trigger" by Instorms!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:36.03,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.39,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad, can I use your guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:39.82,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.38,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.34,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.75,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,At last, Hitori's getting into guitar too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even someone like me can shine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.75,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,if I'm in a band!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.00,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.27,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna learn to play guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.31,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,220)\an8\fnArial Black\c&H615BD2&\b1\shad0.5\bord2\4c&H5352A5&\3c&HE6FEF4&\pos(320,10)}My First Electric Guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.15,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll form a band at school, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:14.15,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\fs16\fad(320,1)\c&H7D6CC0&\3c&HE3E2EA&\bord2\shad0.5\4c&H8883AF&\pos(212,67)}Master the Low Chords \N{\c&HE9EBFF&\3c&HABA6EC&}*Commonly Used Major Chords
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:17.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E, A, G...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all the English?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:26.45,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll play at the culture festival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:29.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and have everyone go crazy for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.51,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(980,1)\b1\pos(320,293.5)\c&HF8EED4&}3 Years Later
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.02,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy... for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.46,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked dark, cramped spaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.83,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd bury my face deep in my hood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.21,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes resented the heartless world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:17.96,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,but yearned for love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.60,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked being soaked by the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.97,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,because my face looked better clouded over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.61,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended to be afraid of the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:32.44,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,while waiting for the sky to burst
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:39.40,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum through the light's distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:43.82,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make thunder roar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:49.62,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum beyond the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:53.75,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:59.81,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum in a harmonizing quartet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:03.80,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cause a revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:09.81,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum in a lamenting forte
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:14.56,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.86,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&H9453D9&\fnImpact\fs30\pos(238.5,132.5)}BOCCHI THE ROCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.86,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&H9453D9&\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\pos(416.5,255)}#01 Lonely Rolling Bocchi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:33.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced six hours every day, so I could \Nlearn how to play in front of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.08,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The result?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:38.47,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Middle school ended, and I \Nnever played a single note for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.00,Congrats,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,191.5)\blur0.4}Congrats on Graduating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I never performed once...
