Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:41.88,Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,At the culture festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I never put together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:44.63,Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,The members for a band!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And I never made a single friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.48,Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,In three whole years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Now, in high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:53.23,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fad(1,104)\c&H727B7C&\bord2.5\pos(311.5,33)\3c&HFBFAF8&}Graduation
