Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:55.02,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta form a band or die trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:05:00.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But despite my vow, it's been a whole month \Nsince high school started,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:02.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and yet my heart remains \Ngrounded in the guitar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:07.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,little better than a shut-in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Lyrics and music by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,From the closet with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:19.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But before I cause neighborhood problems\Nplaying my crummy original song late at night,
