Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I put the effort in, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I brought CDs to school \Nand set them on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.09,FlashbackItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.58,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I bought band merch and showed it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:06.97,FlashbackItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I put in song requests at lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.85,FlashbackItalics,Speaker Voice,0000,0000,0000,,This next song is a request \Nfrom Goto-san in Class 2-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.38,FlashbackItalicsTop,Speaker Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.27,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,...for the death metal song \NI'd been obsessed with lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:16.27,FlashbackItalicsTop,Speaker Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.98,FlashbackItalicsTop,Speaker Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna crush your skuuull!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Not the flashbacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Begone! Begone, filthy memories!
