Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:53.89,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\c&H383C37&\b1\3c&H979B95&\bord2\pos(324,301.5)}Sleep Pipe
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:02.60,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I look... I look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.47,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already a total rocker chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.59,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I look like a real {\i0}somebody{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The people can't look away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:14.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's just gotta talk to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:18.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be all {\i0}over{\i1} this \Nyear's culture festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.18,Default,Boy Student,0000,0000,0000,,So you could see the corgi's butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.52,Default,Girl Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Do we move rooms next period?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.31,Default,Girl Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Science Room B.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.56,Default,Girl Student C,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna karaoke after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.61,Default,Girl Student D,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.60,Default,Girl Student C,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.50,Default,Girl Student D,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder what I should sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Did I go overboard\Nhyping myself up last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:57.75,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm putting out such \Npowerful rocker chick vibes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:08:00.83,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did I end up making myself unapproachable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:03.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a mental breakdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.71,Default,Kita's Friend A,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.58,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(275,138)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1C1E1A&\b1\frz14.3\pos(273.608,142.078)}Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:05.34,Default,Kita's Friend B,0000,0000,0000,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-If they're laughing at me now, \Nit won't just be a mental breakdown,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be mental annihilation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:12.92,Default,Kita's Friend A,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, it's so cute, I've gotta laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.39,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.94,DefaultTop,Kita's Friend B,0000,0000,0000,,My day's immediately better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.52,Default,Kita's Friend B,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kita-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:18.02,Default,Kita's Friend B,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.10,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry! What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You can't put the onus on others \Nand expect perfect results.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:37.76,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,This is a gathering place for \Npeople just as lonely as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:40.09,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that guy's separated from—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.09,DefaultTop,Worker's Daughter,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.71,Default,Worker's Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:44.87,Default,Worker,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.80,DefaultTop,Worker,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's grab dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.14,DefaultTop,Worker,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.14,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They're the perfect freakin' family!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:51.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive my presumptuous empathizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:56.42,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. I broke 30,000 subscribers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:59.44,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The online world is where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorta makes me not wanna go back to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.22,Default,Nijina,0000,0000,0000,,Guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.71,Default,Nijina,0000,0000,0000,,That's a guitar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.77,Default,Nijina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.27,Default,Nijina,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:21.20,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I haven't talked to anyone\Nin so long... my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:23.42,Default,Nijina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sorry to ambush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:26.50,Default,Nijina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nijika Ijichi, second-year \Nat Shimo-Kitazawa High.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.45,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori Goto. Shuka High. First-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me, Hitori-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Right to first names, are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,How good are you at guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.22,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty decent, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.59,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:41.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I'm in kind of a fix here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.18,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do it, that's okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's really okay, but I'm in a real fix...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing okay about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll come right out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:55.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Please, will you play second \Nguitar for my band for today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Band?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:01.18,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a concert coming up, \Nand our guitarist just split!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:04.11,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The song's not too hard! \NYou'll pick it up right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.11,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A concert?! Right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:06.95,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um, err...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.27,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! Let's head to the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even said anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I got dragged along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you come to Shimo-Kita a lot, Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:27.31,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Right, like I've got the courage to visit \Na fashion town for trendy people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost to the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.87,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika-chan's fashionable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:36.40,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's got the real rocker-chick vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.88,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, I'm in a potato-quality tracksuit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,with a real bear of a set of bags under my \Neyes, and a back as arched as a cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do I also smell like mold?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.70,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I spend so much time in the closet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No, I smell like mothballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:52.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Nijika-chan smells great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.38,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She smells just the way \Na high school girl should!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, am I walking too fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:57.80,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:02.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The club we're gonna play at \Nis called Starry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,My big sister's the manager there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.68,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Playing at a club...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.18,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds weirdly legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.06,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's my heart doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:13.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working there part-time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:19.07,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan, are you \Nactually pretty athletic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:24.17,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, but I'm always the last one standing\Nin dodgeball for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Playing in a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't back down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:35.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Remember your daydreams of\Nperforming at the culture festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:40.32,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And your first solo show at Zepp Super Arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:43.11,Default,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori! Hitori! Hitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.71,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the girl who sold out the Budokan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:47.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:53.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't let her think she \Nmade a mistake choosing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.44,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I might've made a mistake choosing her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The dark lands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My first club...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:13.87,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dark... So stuffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.96,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's so soothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.02,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:19.88,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.13,Default,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Could we ask the PA to record again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.51,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's the band that's playing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:25.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I thought bands would be intimidating,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.27,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,They might be a little older than us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:28.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but they're all indoorsy, shy introverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.88,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,After they're done, we'll rehearse too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.15,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They're just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:31.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That there's the PA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.56,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H43F9E9&\fnArial Black\fscy140\fscx90\pos(322,309)}No drinks on the equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.56,DefaultTop,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.62,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive my arrogance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.74,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:40.53,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hitori Goto. Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:46.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I met her in the park by miraculous \Nhappenstance! She's a guitarist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.39,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! Is she glaring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:51.87,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ryo Yamada. She plays bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.90,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Hitori Goto! I'm so very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.75,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.59,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo's just not the expressive type.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.67,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to call her weird! She likes it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.28,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.38,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Seemed like she did...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.74,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, about the manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.98,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,She told you to practice until it was time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.82,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,but instead you snuck out of the club,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:13.36,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,so she got so mad she went out shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:14.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.69,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be in the studio before she comes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.31,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:19.21,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.78,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Real life is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:29.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like there's \Nsome fun stuff coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:33.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Here's today's set list and score.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.16,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where are the other band members?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.82,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,This is everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be doing all instrumentals this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:43.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I can handle this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:46.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Though without any vocals, the playing's \Ngotta be all that much better...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.40,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm supposedly good at guitar. I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.34,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they'll be blown away by my playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:04.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I get pretty good... \Npretty decent reactions online.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:02.86,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take it right from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:06.58,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first time, \Nso we'll run through slow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I even have 30,000 subscribers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.03,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,then we can speed it up \Nas you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can I suck?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.79,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guitarhero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.89,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not totally kidding, but... \NAh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.89,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've got 30,000 subscribers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.47,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:46.23,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(189,1)\b1\c&HE5ECE9&\pos(89,135)}Guitar Man's\NEasy-to-Learn\N Hitori Classes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:41.13,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,In a band, it's super important to be in \Nsync with your fellow live performers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.94,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,But Hitori has social anxiety \Nand can't make eye contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.67,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,and she'll be inclined to \Nrush ahead of the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.03,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,She might be an awesome solo player,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:51.74,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HEFF4EE&\fs18\pos(272.5,80)}God
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:51.74,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b1\c&HEFF4EE&\pos(213.5,126)}Social Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:51.74,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HEFF4EE&\fs18\pos(189.5,177.5)}Normal Person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:51.74,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HEFF4EE&\fs18\pos(175,233)}Water Flea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:51.74,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HEFF4EE&\fs18\pos(165,288.5)}Hitori
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:51.74,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,but when in a band, she's sub-water-flea \Nlevel, the worst there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:54.28,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. I'm Plankton Goto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:57.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She sounds like an unfunny comedian!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:59.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, Hitori Goto turned to dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.96,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and never picked up a guitar again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.63,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnImpact\fs32\shad2.5\pos(489.5,265)}BOCCHI THE ROCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.63,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnImpact\fs40\pos(320,73)}THE                               END
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:11.01,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\move(205.14,333.34,204,174.5,23,4653)\b1}Water Flea                Hitori Goto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:11.01,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\move(205.14,376.34,204,217.5,23,4653)\b1}Drummer                  Nijika Ijichi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:11.01,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\move(205.14,420.84,204,262,23,4653)\b1}Bassist                       Ryo Yamada
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:11.01,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\move(205.14,466.84,204,308,23,4653)\b1}Guitar Man              As Himself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.01,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The show's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.52,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I c-c-can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.18,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault! \NWe just came together today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm very good either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.77,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}very{\i0} good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at me, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.14,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here in reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like I could\Ndo the intro or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:36.57,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I could offer up my life \Nto put on a harakiri show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:39.49,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They'll at least remember\Nthe name of the band, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.88,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I sucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:41.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little {\i1}too{\i0} rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.45,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:47.13,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,If they boo you, I'll give \Nthem a bonk with my bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.13,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,977)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H3400D5&\3c&HE5E9E8&\pos(320,49.834)\bord2\shad2}Bonk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:50.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Does a bass make such a fancy noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, bloodshed is pretty rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.63,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.73,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You can't justify everything with "rock"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:16:00.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it'll probably just be my \Nfriends who come to watch us play!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:03.63,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,And Nijika is my only friend, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:07.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Normal high school girls \Ndon't know good music from bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of take could get you \Nin trouble on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? So just chill!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.76,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I d-dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.55,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} know good music from bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.54,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that wasn't a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.14,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.46,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We can't force her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:29.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to push you so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.17,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:37.05,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I r-really was happy you reached out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've wanted to be in a band for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.47,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I couldn't get the people together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:46.52,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,So I just upload covers \Nto the internet instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.19,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you usually play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:51.23,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mostly songs by popular bands \Nfrom the last few years,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:54.26,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,so I could play them right away \Nonce the band got together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:54.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.80,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.38,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's the reason I'm the way I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:02.75,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Being in a band with other people \Nwas a pipe dream after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Covering all popular songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She sounds like guitarhero-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:08.46,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.63,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably about our age, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,guitarhero...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:18.30,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(277,472)\fnArial\fs11\c&H3B403A&\frz4.371\fax-0.25\pos(114,115.5)}[Guitar] Acid "Spring Snow" [Gave it a try]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:18.30,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(277,472)\fnArial\fs11\c&H3B403A&\frz4.371\fax-0.25\pos(120.5,145.5)}Views: 1,012
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:18.30,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(277,472)\an4\fnArial\fs12\c&H474E49&\fax-0.24\bord3\3c&HFDFFFD&\frz3.908\pos(65.5,217)}Sorry I can't upload very often nowadays!\NThere's just so much going on at high school!\NNext time I'll try a song I do all the time\Nwith my friends at karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:18.30,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(277,472)\an4\fnArial\fs11\c&H9DA09D&\fax-0.24\frz2.074\pos(45.5,305)}10 comments                                      Sort
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you a link if you haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:18.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She's super awesome! You should hear her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.08,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Awe... some?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:23.75,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,She comes up in my recommendations \Na lot, so I've seen her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.14,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,She really is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.94,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Though her naming sense is a bit cringy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:33.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I follow her with notifications on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to play with her some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You just did, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:41.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Look, what I'm getting at here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,is that even awesome, popular people \Nare out there playing guitar,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:48.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,lots and lots of them,\Nin places we're not even watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch her later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,\NI think you'll get what I mean\Nif you watch the videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:18:00.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I always figured real-life people \Ndidn't care about me at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:05.94,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You can't give up on playing in a band \Njust because it didn't work out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible it's our problem, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.00,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Our problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.09,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:14.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But someone this nice has been \Nwatching me all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and actually spoke to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.24,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,She stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:22.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's the kind of miracle \Nmost people never experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let it go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.50,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you want to perform after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.32,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I know all that, rationally...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:37.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still too scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.39,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can play \Nin front of an audience...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.33,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,If you're scared, \Nyou could play from in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:44.31,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(315,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs18\b1\c&H4144D1&\3c&HA5C1F0&\bord2\fax-0.05\frz3.591\pos(186,291)}Ripe Mangos
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.56,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs36\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord2.5\pos(328,198.5)}Ripe Mangos
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the same environment \Nthat I play in all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.19,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Where exactly do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:56.15,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs28\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord2\pos(330,51.5)}Ripe Mangos
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:54.64,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,How you feelin' tonight, Shimo-Kita?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.15,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,She's suddenly more outgoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:59.48,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how do you \Nwant us to introduce you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:02.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,"Hitori-chan"? Should we use your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:03.90,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'd... I'd rather not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Any nicknames, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:09.02,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,In middle school, they called me \N"Hey" and "You there"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think those are nicknames!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:14.79,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew anyone well enough \Nto get nicknames from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.22,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.94,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Hitoribocchi (all alone)...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.12,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,How about Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.18,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Another tactless comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.29,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm B-B-Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.14,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She likes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's just my first ever nickname...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,This is making me teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.03,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you haven't told me your band name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.63,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kessoku Band.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.02,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Kessoku Band...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the word for "zip tie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.57,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.82,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's the worst pun! \NWe're totally changing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.60,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Why? It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.81,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:52.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Band name aside, it's time to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:58.55,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The key is to have fun, even if you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings really come \Nout in your playing, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:07.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We can always work on the \Nskill part next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:07.72,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Next... time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:10.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.38,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:15.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They're okay with there being a next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you! We're Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We'll play a bunch of \Nsongs you probably know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.32,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,so please enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.70,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:41.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that I can't play as \Nwell as I usually do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:46.39,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,playing in a band with other \Npeople is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've never really shone before today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And I still don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:57.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,This might actually be a low point for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.88,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.80,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Your intro bombed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:05.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.53,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-B...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.39,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-B-B-B...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you're freaking me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:17.01,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-Before our next performance, I'm gonna get \Nbrave enough to say hello to my classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What a dramatic declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.25,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Such growth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:22.32,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:26.55,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's have a Bocchi-chan-welcome-party-\Nslash-concert-post-mortem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:30.26,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm pretty exhausted from \Nall this social interaction, so I'm gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.85,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.76,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.22,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,There's no "ties" in this band at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get over my social anxiety
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:54.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and bring out my full guitarhero powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:57.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,For Nijika-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:21:59.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:01.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:04.96,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3572,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H41403D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\bord2\shad2\4c&H00C6F3&\pos(309,49.5)}#02 See You Tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:39.75,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!